7/58ca/196464_mini.png?m=1535078743","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9897/58ca/196464_mini.png?m=1535078743","location":null,"btc":null,"id":196464},"last_reply_by":"alect","last_touched":1628820482,"title":"关于移动宽带+百度网盘","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/795491","created":1628819013,"content":"情况概要：\r\n1.最近用移动积分兑换了 1000M 宽带两个月体验卡\r\n2.以前是 200M，所以家里的猫是支持 1000M 的。\r\n3.路由器是华硕 ax86U,实际使用也是能跑到 1000M\r\n\r\n\r\n问题：\r\n1.打开百度网盘，同时开 5 个下载任务，一开始下载速度在 20-30mb/s 附近，过了十几秒家里的网就会断\r\n2.跟 ax86u 无关，因为我把台式与猫直连也能复现\r\n3.与台式无关，因为在 mac 上也能复现\r\n4.只开一个下载任务，昨天试了一小时，未发现断网，且下载速度维持在 26mb/s 左右\r\n\r\n有大神遇到过这种情况嘛？","content_rendered":"<p>情况概要：\n1.最近用移动积分兑换了 1000M 宽带两个月体验卡\n2.以前是 200M，所以家里的猫是支持 1000M 的。\n3.路由器是华硕 ax86U,实际使用也是能跑到 1000M</p>\n<p>问题：\n1.打开百度网盘，同时开 5 个下载任务，一开始下载速度在 20-30mb/s 附近，过了十几秒家里的网就会断\n2.跟 ax86u 无关，因为我把台式与猫直连也能复现\n3.与台式无关，因为在 mac 上也能复现\n4.只开一个下载任务，昨天试了一小时，未发现断网，且下载速度维持在 26mb/s 左右</p>\n<p>有大神遇到过这种情况嘛？</p>\n","last_modified":1628819013,"replies":8,"id":795491},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1620107025","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1620107025","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":9641,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1620107025","stars":5079,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"bibiisme","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1c050cee048f04edca8a2014f70479a8?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/bibiisme","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1557321301,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1c050cee048f04edca8a2014f70479a8?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1c050cee048f04edca8a2014f70479a8?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":410425},"last_reply_by":"quzard","last_touched":162